properties.name: Back in the Loop
properties.description:
Coming off of a series of repeat rides, we cannot escape the feeling that we have been somehow out of the loop. It has been a great time, of course, but it is as if, by returning to those earlier rides, we have been missing out on all the new places we could have been riding in the past couple months. Or perhaps, since we have been repeating ourselves, you could say that we have actually been in a loop, like some kind of Star Trek episode or Bill Murray movie? No matter. Even if it is a bit unclear where we have been in relation to the proverbial loop, this week, we will most certainly be back in at least one actual, non-proverbial loop and adjacent to one kind-of sort-of proto-loop.
